# Gmail MCP Server Environment Configuration

# Path to your Google OAuth2 credentials JSON file
# Download from Google Cloud Console > APIs & Services > Credentials
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=C:\path\to\your\credentials.json

# Optional: Custom download directory (defaults to Downloads folder)
# GMAIL_DOWNLOAD_PATH=C:\custom\download\path

# Optional: Gmail account to use (for multi-account setups)
# GMAIL_ACCOUNT=your-email@gmail.com